name: JCPOA Signatures

desc.html:
Signatures on the Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action (JCPOA) document
On the top left side, there is a Persian handwriting by Mohammad Javad Zarif, which reads: مخلص عباس‌آقا و مجيدآقا. Translation: [I am] Sincere to Mr. Abbas [Araqchi] and Mr. Majid [Takht-Ravanchi].
